25 Break Up Quotes About Lost Loves And New Beginnings by Just Promise Rings

We can't help who we fall in love with and sometimes relationships just don't work out like we had first hoped and the old break up quote "when one door closes, another door opens" still rings just as true today when it comes to relationship break ups.

So many people feel completely lost after a break up, like life is just never going to be the same anymore, feeling like they'll never fall in love again and can't stop missing their ex
